##Ordinary Li Wenliang

Wechat, renwumag1980

Feature Introduction, the best Chinese character report

He once made a New Year's wish, the New Year hopes to be a simple person, see the world miscellaneous but do not leave traces in the heart, maintain enough common heart. He also said that the unexamined life is not worth living, I hope we can achieve their values, share. His wechat signature is, "theory is gray, the tree of life is evergreen. ".

By Luo Ting, Yang Zhou, Luo Qian

Editor, sugar maple

1

Last night at 11 o'clock, "people" reporters rushed to the Wuhan Central Hospital after the Lake Hospital district of the hospital building, Li Wenliang two college students have been waiting there for half an hour. They were also doctors from Wuhan, who had come to see him on behalf of the whole class. As it was past visiting time, the entrance to the hospital building had been blocked and could not be entered.

Late at night, the building is still very bright, the second floor is the ICU is rescuing Li Wenliang, a few floors above, living with his infected parents. Students worried about them, call Li Wenliang father, hope to go up to accompany. But hospital staff, who were with his father, declined the request over the phone. Then they spoke to Li Wenliang's pregnant wife, who was out of town. She was worried and worried, but didn't know the latest information. They told her, "if I hear anything, you'll be the first to know. ". "

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Wuhan Central Hospital building

It was just after midnight, and the hospital was continuing to rescue Li Wenliang. But one of the nurses in the building, dressed very thinly, went down to the first floor alone and burst into tears. First against the wall, then on the floor crying. Even standing more than 10 meters away, the sound of crying is clear and audible, echoing in the quiet hospital at night.

Students talked about Li Wenliang's illness. Li Wenliang had been interviewed by the media a few days earlier and seemed to be in good spirits. But in fact, for more than ten days, Li Wenliang has not been discharged from the breathing machine. His classmates said, "this is a very bad omen. "

Yesterday afternoon, Li Wenliang was transferred from the Nanjing Road Hospital area of Wuhan Central Hospital to the Houhu hospital area because, according to the student, he already needed ECMO, but the Central Hospital, the Nanjing Road Hospital district, was not in Florida, and all of their equipment was transferred to Golden Pond Hospital. And then there's one in the back of the lake that could save his life. But there's an online version of it, too, which says the machine was borrowed from another hospital.

Is His condition so serious that he needs an external lung? The student said, in fact, it's long overdue. "

Wu Yan, a doctor at the Central Hospital, told people late last night that Li Wenliang was in poor condition after being transferred to the hospital yesterday afternoon. Turned around at night, and within seconds, he was breathing in and out, stopped breathing, no vitals for three hours, but he was still on Ecmo, and now he's not being declared dead. "

"Even though I know he's probably gone, I'm still hoping that the Internet rumors are true and that ECMO can work miracles. "At 00:43 this morning, the doctor told people.

"Everything I've learned tells me it's impossible, but I've always thought it's possible. The doctor explained, with his medical common sense, that "breathing into the heart stopped for three hours, normally enough to be declared clinically dead. But we got an Ecmo to keep the cycle going. "

At 2 a.m. , Caixin Media reported, the rescue was still under way. At 3:48 am, an official at Wuhan Central Hospital sent a message: Li Wenliang, an ophthalmologist at the COVID-19, died at 2:58 am on February 7,2020, after trying his best to rescue the unfortunate infection. Three hours of ECMO, at least three hours of ECMO, no miracle.

Earlier, at 23:25 last night, the World Health Organization had tweeted: "We are deeply saddened by the death of Dr. Li Wenliang. ". All of us should praise him for his work on the COVID-19. "

Dr Li Wenliang

2

Li Wenliang's college classmates told people that on the afternoon of December 30,2019, Li Wenliang told everyone in their class group: "seven cases of SARS have been confirmed in the south China fruit and seafood market. " half an hour later, he added, "the latest news is that the coronavirus infection has been confirmed and the virus typing is under way. Keep your family on their toes. "

As doctors, they believed in Li Wenliang. He has been in the business for many years, and his judgment is not likely to be wrong. Because of Li Wenliang's warning, they began to make protection, began to stock N95 masks, also began to wear protective clothing at work. Not a lot of people knew that back then, so masks were easy to buy. It was this supply that protected some of the doctors at the beginning of the outbreak and helped them cope with shortages later on.

After Li Wenliang was admonished, the students all knew. They are more cautious, no longer talk about the new virus on Wechat, but will still spread orally, especially many of the 80's young doctors, know that they are starting to do protection. So he really saved a lot of people. "

Before being reprimanded, Li Wenliang was not a well-known doctor in the hospital. Wu Yan, a young doctor in another department, had barely heard of him and had never met him. I only knew about it because he was rumoured, he was reprimanded, we were all upset about him, and then we heard he was infected... he was punished and infected, and the family was sick. I hear it's a lot of pressure. And we were all so happy when he came out of it. "

He admired Li Wenliang's courage in his heart. "All I know is that he told the truth and said things that many people were afraid to say. But the punishment was disproportionate, and the body and mind were traumatized. "

That night, Dr. Wu Yan's circle of friends was "blown away by candles. ". Although Li was not pronounced dead at the time of his interview with people, his heart had stopped for three hours. "We all know that when we mourn for Dr. Li, we mourn for ourselves, " Wu said. "

At 1 a.m. , Li's college classmates were still shuttling through locked hospital buildings, searching for passageways that might still be open. They wanted to go up to the floor where Li's parents were hospitalized, at least to see if they were okay. But after two hours of trying, nothing worked.

As they search for an exit, they pass a wall with the glorious history of Wuhan Central Hospital, and another wall with the hospital's motto: The hospital is devoted to saving the lives of the wounded, the sick, and the dying, one of the most valuable lessons of all is awe and love. Respect for life is to treat patients like relatives, care for the health of patients, people-oriented, to the staff in good faith.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Li Wenliang's portrait on Renren. com

3

Dr. Li Wenliang's micro blog records his daily life, both vivid and ordinary.

He likes to eat, often joking about his "appetite in the tiger, " the thought of eating oranges, wearing slippers to run 1,000 meters to buy to eat, see the ice cream shop all kinds of ice cream, will sigh, "Damn, too many temptations" ; Izakaya and Haidilao are his love, he said he loved mustard and Sashimi. Fried Chicken is also his love, Dicos's pistol leg, which he orders every time he goes to the train station, he describes it as 'delicious' -- a large leg attached to the crotch, satisfying to look at, crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, paired with an exclusive dry plate, it is the ultimate in legs! Another coke at this point, and I feel like I'm at the top of my game.

He watched drama, like "Qingyunian" , also star, recently more like Xiao Zhan, think Xiao Zhan handsome, sing "green light" especially good. Car Li Son 158 yuan a catty, he will tease oneself can not afford to eat, bought a few tangerines spent 30 yuan, called himself "Diaosi" , laments the hardships of life. He also likes to retweet the lottery tweets, the retweet of the lottery phone, the retweet of the lottery car and the retweet of the lottery car. Finally, one time, he didn't do the lottery insulator, and won a box of wet wipes. He thanks the donors by sending his special tweet.

Being a doctor is very hard work. He sometimes complains about his work. "I'm so tired, " he says, "I don't want to work anymore. " He complains about working for three days. "I'm going to die, " "I hate the clinic, " and he looks forward to eating pot roast after work, but it really let him leave, he could not bear to take off the white coat on his body, his mind is, "the patient abused me a thousand times, I treat the patient like the first love. ".

If you look at his micro-blog, you'll find him a bit cute. The ophthalmologist seems to have a little boy inside of him, laughing and cursing on social media. "Fuck You" , "I'll go" and "fuck you" are all on his lips, he even thinks, "does it hurt when a chicken lays an egg? " And takes a picture of a butterfly, posting it on social media with the caption: a butterfly. In his free time, he also likes to go out, watch canola and play badminton. If someone calls him "uncle" on the way, he will be "mad" and feel "hurt" . He also likes practical jokes, when you check out of a hotel, you fold the covers into the shape of someone inside to scare the waiter.

If you ask him what his favorite season is, it should be autumn, he likes the autumn morning, the Sun through the leaves, the ground to cast a little bit of shadow. He once described the autumn in Wuhan as a kind of mild and mild, in which you can feel the driest rain and the softest wind, and of course you can feel the falling leaves falling on the ground, the beauty and the thrill of stepping on it.

Dr. Li shared warm moments with his family. The weather was fine, his wife and children were with him, his parents came to visit him, and when they left on the high-speed train, he would take pictures of the trains they were on.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Li Wenliang's friendster cover

But at the same time, he was a man who cared about society. He spoke for Wang Qinglei, the outspoken host of the Wenzhou train accident, and asked for signatures to reinstate Wang. On February 1, he gave an interview to Caixin. Even though he had been admonished and infected himself and his parents, he bravely said, "a healthy society should not have only one voice. ". "

The same day, his nucleic acid test came back positive. He said: 'The dust has settled, the diagnosis has been confirmed, and there's a dog's face. "thank you for your support. I have not lost my license. Please rest assured that I will actively cooperate with the treatment and try to get out of the hospital as soon as possible.

Before that, when the working group called for doctors to apply to the front line of the epidemic, he also said: "I am ready to apply. ". In another picture circulating on the Internet, someone asked him on Wechat: What are your plans after you recover from your illness? He said: good on the line, the epidemic is still spreading, do not want to be a deserter.
